Package infotrader.parser.exception

All exceptions defined by gedcom4j are found in this package.

See: Description

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InfoTraderParserException
    An exception thrown by the parser indicating inability to deal with the input file
    InfoTraderValidationException
    An exception indicating that the process of validation failed.
    InfoTraderWriterException
    A base exception class for when the GedcomWriter fails
    InfoTraderWriterVersionDataMismatchException
    Represents a mismatch between the data being written and the GEDCOM version under which it's supposed to be written...
    ParserCancelledException
    Exception indicating that the file load/parse operation was cancelled
    UnsupportedInfoTraderCharsetException
    Represents an unsupported/illegal value for a charset encoding in a GEDCOM file
    UnsupportedVersionException
    An exception for when an unsupported GEDCOM version is used
    WriterCancelledException
    Exception indicating that the file construction and writing operation was cancelled
